 The Middelburg community was left in shock after a group of armed robbers brazenly opened fire during a CIT heist, in broad daylight, placing numbers of unsuspecting shoppers in danger. In the video, the G4S transit vehicle can be seen ramming into the attackers’ vehicle, in an attempt to put a stop to the full-blown assault. Also read: Update: Man shot in Midwater heist succumbs to his wounds The armed suspects managed to flee the scene before police arrived.
